family ip
  note: noflush -- existing built-in/undeclared rules kept; declared user chains overwritten; policies applied
  note: noflush -- counts are the net positional diff; apply re-appends listed rules to unflushed chains, so live rules overlapping the config are duplicated
  + -p tcp --dport 80 -j ACCEPT
  Plan: 1 to add, 0 to remove, 0 policy changes
